<p>Viewing work package progress</p><p>Quickly see where the work packages are in the work flow. 
  </p> 
	  
		<p> Within the 
		  Dashboard, the 
		  Work Package Time Line provides you with a visual
		  display of all the active work packages in a work flow. The work packages are
		  displayed as balls and are grouped into the stages of the selected work flow.
		  Using the filters, you can change the view based on release, iteration, work
		  flow, or resource. 
		 
	 </p> 
	  
		 
		   Select your product from the drop-down at the top of the
			 Dashboard tab. 
		   
		   
			 <p>The Dashboard is refreshed and
				shows status information for the selected product. 
			 </p> 
		   
		
		  
		   
		  
		 
		 
		   Select your desired release, iteration, work flow, or resource in
			 the 
			 Work Package Time Line area. 
		   
		   
			 <p>The active work packages matching your selections are displayed. 
			 </p> 
		   
		 
		  Hover over a work package to see its details. 
		   
		 
	   
		<p> Active work packages are displayed
		  in the various work flow states. 
		</p> 
	  
  